observationText: The NF90-8 cell line had a highly gained region in chromosome 4 containing the PDGFRA and KIT receptors.
The 90-8TL cell line exhibited downregulation of miR-145-5p, let-7b-5p, and miR-143-3p compared to the cutaneous neurofibroma cell line HS53T.
The 90-8TL cell line exhibited upregulation of miR-135b-5p and miR-889-3p compared to the cutaneous neurofibroma cell line HS53T.
The 90-8 cell line exhibited complete loss of heterozygosity with no detectable DNA from the wild-type NF1 allele.
